{"tid":777471,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"JC《好聲音》唱功迴響大","createTime":"2018-08-13T02:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T05:00:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"664bd29afea28a0e5f090879fb8f1c5c4e64f165","tid":777471,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:41:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180813/20474948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180813%2F20474948&d=QwPp060cUdNSOk1CN8PejHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=4b3b5e0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180813%2F20474948&h=dc2d5d8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180813/20474948</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月13日 <br />\n<br />\nJC《好聲音》唱功迴響大<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180813/large/13ec2p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180813%2Flarge%2F13ec2p7.jpg&h=57722973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■JC日前現身內地節目再唱成名作，因而獲得不少迴響。微博圖片<br />\n<br />\n陳詠桐（JC）於16年被黎明睇中簽約成旗下藝人，18歲時出道作《說散就散》在YouTube成為當時年十大熱門音樂影片之一，於一個月內獲過百萬觀看人次，被讚巨肺兼有唱功，可惜在頒獎禮上無功而還，星途一直平淡。<br />\n<br />\n日前JC現身內地節目《中國好聲音》，再唱成名作《說散就散》，得到不少迴響。JC是實力派歌手，當她表演過後，引起網民熱烈討論，更獲不少人稱讚：「有實力就只差機會了，希望她找到伯樂」、「她唱的好好」、「唱出故事了」、「應該很多人也是看了這個才知道原唱長怎樣吧」、「很好！現在我記住你了」等。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：唐如  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n谷祖琳關懷情緒病患者<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【馮仁昭四圍超】傅嘉莉爭氣奪廚神"},{"pid":"61d3ff9ffb368090027cb169b27c017079a451ef","tid":777471,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:43:02.000Z","msg":"翻版gem 越反越紅 <br />\nbtw who"},{"pid":"8fb4289129aee50b17cf6b7498fa2cfee5ab8194","tid":777471,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:57:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3401c5bd456baced9c45c5ada788d0973d1d0ad","tid":777471,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fb4289129aee50b17cf6b7498fa2cfee5ab8194","tid":777471,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"61d3ff9ffb368090027cb169b27c017079a451ef","tid":777471,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:43:02.000Z","msg":"翻版gem 越反越紅 <br />\nbtw who"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:57:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:05:43.000Z","msg":"黎明都有打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3ed6f90061f84f45147981c723e8c58128444e","tid":777471,"uid":33104,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:10:10.000Z","msg":"簽黎明真係對耐性同EQ既考驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bb1870c6dcbb9a84d6e4ad7098a9255cfddcbc","tid":777471,"uid":111814,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:20:25.000Z","msg":"想紅第二步，盡快離開黎明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2836681feb3a7b075bae7dc4be71b80efb6216","tid":777471,"uid":954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:28:28.000Z","msg":"深圳好多街邊店都播緊佢d 歌"},{"pid":"fe78f8cc12c0ab27e21899691b78a6f1bb74e6a2","tid":777471,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:29:06.000Z","msg":"好掂"},{"pid":"07081305f5d9c7ba6b56f86ff686cbce0e8d53a9","tid":777471,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:29:28.000Z","msg":"黎明條曲街害左幾多星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0701ca55f6ef6ff61af07889e3adfc4bbb741445","tid":777471,"uid":2901,"like